@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Air Transport Company Collaborator" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC

ATCC -> System : Requests to decommission an aircraft

activate System
System --> ATCC : Requests company and aircraft identification
deactivate System

ATCC -> System : Provides company and aircraft identification

activate System
System --> System : Check if collaborator is authorized
System --> System : Validate air transport company
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to company
System --> System : Validate aircraft
System --> System : Check if aircraft belongs to company fleet
System --> System : Check pending flights
System --> System : Validate current operational status

alt aircraft can be decommissioned
    System --> System : Update aircraft operational status
    System --> ATCC : Aircraft decommissioned successfully
else aircraft cannot be decommissioned
    System --> ATCC : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate ATCC

@enduml